50|$|The Phoenix Garden {{has survived}} various challenges, {{including}} a major industrial <b>fly-tipping</b> incident soon after its foundation. It {{is the only}} one of the original seven Covent Garden Community Gardens to survive to this day. It continues to be run by a committee of volunteers comprising local residents and workers.|$|E
